nIlavastrogracAriRI          azwAdaSaBujA pOtrI SivadUtI yamasvasA   sunandA vikacA lambA jayantI nakulAkulA          vilaNkA nandinI nandA nandayantI niraYjanA   kAlaMjarI SatamuKI vikarAlI karAlikA nIlavastrogracAriRI          azwAdaSaBujA pOtrI SivadUtI yamasvasA   sunandA vikacA lambA jayantI nakulAkulA          vilaNkA nandinI nandA nandayantI niraYjanA   kAlaMjarI SatamuKI vikarAlI karAlikA nIlavastrogracAriRI          azwAdaSaBujA pOtrI SivadUtI yamasvasA   sunandA vikacA lambA jayantI nakulAkulA          vilaNkA nandinI nandA nandayantI niraYjanA   kAlaMjarI SatamuKI vikarAlI karAlikA          virajAH puralA jIrI bahuputrI kuleSvarI   kEwaBI kAladamanI dardurA kuladevatA          rOdrI kundrA mahArOdrI kAlaMgamA mahAniSA   baladevasvasA putrI hIrI kzemaMkarI praBA          mArI hEmavatI cApi golA SiKaravAsinI

        virajAH puralA jIrI bahuputrI kuleSvarI   kEwaBI kAladamanI dardurA kuladevatA          rOdrI kundrA mahArOdrI kAlaMgamA mahAniSA   baladevasvasA putrI hIrI kzemaMkarI praBA          mArI hEmavatI cApi golA SiKaravAsinI

hEmavatI cApi golA SiKaravAsinI

hakkAraka :: devakARqaH hakkAraka puM AkAra puM hUtO hakkArakAkArO ca caRqAlAnAM tu vallakI          kARqavIRA kuvIRA ca qakkArI kiMnarI taTA   sArikA KuNKaRI cATa dardare kalasImuKaH          sUtrakoRo qamarukaM samO paRavakikaRO   SfNgavAdye SfNgamuKaM huqukkastAlamardalaH          kAhalA tu kuhAlA syAccaRqako lAhalA ca sA   saMveSapratiboDArDe dragaqadrakawAvuBO          devatArcanatUrye tu DUmalo valirityapi   kzullakaM mftayAtrAyAM maNgale priyavAdikA          raRodyame tvarDatUro vAdyaBedAstaTApare   qiRqimo JarJaro maqustimilA kirikiccikA          lambikA wawwarI veDyA kalApUrAdayo'pi ca
